     C*
     C           RRN1      IFEQ 9999
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     END
     C*
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C           RRN1      IFEQ *ZERO
     C                     CLEARSFL010
     C                     Z-ADD1         RRN1
